---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const studies = [
  {
    index: '001',
    title: '雾、墨与长阅读',
    source: 'Dark Thoughts · Never Enough',
    summary: '把编辑式的长文排版、暖色日夜主题与颗粒化画布，重组为一页属于 Ryanyx 的博客实验。',
    tags: ['Editorial', 'Canvas', 'Theme'],
    href: '/projects/frontend-collection/dark-thoughts-inspired/',
    state: '已收录'
  }
];
---
<BaseLayout title="有趣前端收藏" description="收集、复刻与拆解那些值得驻足的网页前端。" lang="zh" path="projects" switchTo="/en/projects/frontend-collection/">
  <section class="collection-hero">
    <div class="collection-kicker">A SMALL MUSEUM OF WEB ATMOSPHERE</div>
    <p class="collection-count">{String(studies.length).padStart(2, '0')} / 持续生长</p>
    <h1>有趣前端<br /><em>收藏</em></h1>
    <p class="collection-lead">一些网页会让人放慢鼠标：不是因为功能更复杂，而是它们把字体、节奏、材质和交互编排成了一种气氛。这里收录这种瞬间，也把它们拆开，做成可以学习的原创实验。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="collection-list" aria-label="前端收藏条目">
    {studies.map((study) => (
      <a class="collection-entry" href={study.href}>
        <span class="collection-index">{study.index}</span>
        <div class="collection-entry-main">
          <div class="collection-entry-meta"><span>{study.state}</span><span>{study.source}</span></div>
          <h2>{study.title}</h2>
          <p>{study.summary}</p>
          <div class="collection-tags">{study.tags.map((tag) => <span>{tag}</span>)}</div>
        </div>
        <span class="collection-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    ))}
  </section>

  <aside class="collection-note">
    <span>收录原则</span>
    <p>不搬运页面或素材。每一项只提炼其可学习的设计结构，再以新的内容、代码和视觉资产重做；原始灵感与技术观察会在条目中明确标注。</p>
  </aside>
</BaseLayout>
